title: Big Brother Naija: Bisola, Gifty, CocoIce, 2 more housemates are up for possible eviction
text: Tweet Following Soma and Miyonse's eviction on Sunday, February 5, 2017 , 12 housemates in the Big Brother Naija house were left to vote during the Live Nomination show. After the nomination show, Biggie announced to the Housemates that the housemates up for possible eviction this weekend are Bisola, Bassey, CocoIce, Debie-Rise and TTT. However, with Efe's Head of House power, he saved TTT and replaced him with Gifty . Last week, Soma, Gifty and Miyonse were nominated for possible eviction. CocoIce had used her Head of House power to save Gifty and replaced her with Efe.
